{
  "stem": "20405.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Which, this Jewish guy who was a traitor, he looked like he was God.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was thinking like he was God.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because he had everything over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we had-- across the street of the synagogue was a kind of a hospital for the-- for crazy people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Over there, what he did, he got a friend of him, a big guy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was going to the Germans, where are the rich people?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "With their names, he knew their names, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came then to-- into the-- the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And bring him down to this hospital, down, very-- those rooms, for the crazy, they had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And his friend with a leather-- what do you call 'em, the--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whip.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With a leather it, he was hitting all those Jewish guy to-- to-- to find out where they hide their gold.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is the way this guy, Hason name, name of the-- this Jewish traitor, like I told you-- which, they killed him at the end, the Jewish guys killed him-- was taking all the-- all this gold from them.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this Hason gave him this gold to the-- to this guy, to Vichencelli.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember his first name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was a-- was a young guy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- not too tall, was almost short.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not-- well, a medium size. = had another brother in his family, which he sent them to the concentration camps in Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was, like I said, like a god over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Going out with a single horse outside of the-- of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Going out around Thessaloniki like he was a very rich guy and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, well, I'm glad they killed him at the end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Me?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
